text: The Mummy and the Hummingbird is a lost 1915 American silent drama movie directed by James Durkin and starring Charles Cherry, Arthur Hoops, Lillian Tucker, Claire Zobelle, Nina Lindsey. It was distributed by Paramount Pictures. ==Other websites== * Category:1915 drama movies Category:American silent movies Category:American drama movies Category:Paramount Pictures movies
